* General flags:
	-F config directory
	-U authcID
	-X authzID
	-b suffix (slapacl: entryDN)
	-c continue mode
	-d debug level
	-f config file
	-l LDIF file
	-n database number
	-q "quick" mode
	-s subtree
	-u dryrun (slappasswd: RFC2307 userPassword)
	-v verbose

